Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:21.50,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rage on! Rage on! Rage on! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:21.50,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Moeagare! Moeagare! Moeagare GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:27.75,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must run forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:27.75,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo hashire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:34.76,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,If you are still burning with furious rage...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:34.76,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Mada ikari ni moeru toshi ga aru nara...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must fight the towering foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kyodai na teki o
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uteyo! Uteyo! Uteyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Bring to bear the rage of justice, Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Seigi no ikari o butsukero GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Rise once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru! Yomigaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As the White Base fled Side 6...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Conscon Mobile Unit\Ncontinued its relentless attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the Gundam and other machines,\Nthey were able to fight off the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the full-scale battle\Nhas yet to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Glory of Solomon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.35,0:02:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Fleet approaching us\Nfrom the stern!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- White Base, do you read me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're entering formation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll align in formation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prepare to receive supplies.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Tell him we acknowledge.\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Columbus supply ship coming into our bow\Nfrom starboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them to load the supplies quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go pay a visit to the fleet commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How come I'm not allowed to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna say hi to the commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no errand for children!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them treat you\Nlike a child either, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.93,0:02:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant, help out with the supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some ugly-looking thing\Ncarrying missiles, but what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Public-type assault ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Assault ship?!\NMeaning we've got tough times ahead still.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't like this one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right. I'll leave it to you.\N- Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The captain of the White Base has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Junior Grade Bright Noa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well, Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you again,\NCommandant Wakkein.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Commandant" isn't necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm with the top brass,\NI'm quickly reduced to a minor officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.16,0:03:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're starting to look like a real commander.\NVery admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Look at this.\N- Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the course we're presently on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our main forces are taking a wide detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So the target of the operation is Solomon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base will join us at\Nthe vanguard in our attack on Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? That's a big responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we up to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you're able\Nto look at it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...proves just how confident you've become.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But, sir. The White Base pilots\Nare all tremendously overworked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Especially Amuro.\N- Oh, the Gundam kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He possesses an amazing talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- He's different from us.\N- Different? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The magnetic pressure won't increase.\NThat's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dinner's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Just leave it there, please?\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one Big Zam on the Papua?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!\NAt present, that's all they...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is my brother thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rick Doms we have won't be sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not send us 10 Doms\Ninstead of one cutting-edge mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes?!\N- This Big Zam is still in the prototype stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They're rushing development, but they\Nhave so many requests from every front...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's enough. Dismissed.\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Assemble the Big Zam on the double!\N- Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't we located the Tianem Fleet yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid not, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:06:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're searching where the Minovsky particle\Ndensity is high, but with so many decoys...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you expect in a war?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.65,0:06:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up with the supply loading!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Disengage conveyor pipes! Close off valves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Check the internal air pressure at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the harbor pilot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Prosecutor Cameron.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you removed the weapon seals for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've removed the seals,\Nbut firing within Side 6 airspace is still...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll leave soon.\NI don't want you to come here ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Be careful with your words, Mr. Cameron.\N- Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Side 6 has survived this long\Nbecause it's convenient for Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd do well to remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that we live by your whim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah. What's taking you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that young lady...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She's like a sister.\NLet's leave it at that, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our fleet Is currently situated{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...from the enemy space fortress, Solomon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so close to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From here on, nothing stands between{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Changing fleet formation to lateral line!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow!\NWhere are Katz, Letz, Kikka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In E-Block of the gravitational core.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Haro, too?\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have to stay here and be quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't fight unless we have these on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll make a frontal attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our Public assault shipserence field.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All vessels proceed directly ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gotta be kidding. With a fleet this small,\Nthis is practically suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'll be fine, Mr. Kai.s worked out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy for you to say, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough out of you, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to put our faith\Nin Tianem's main fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You only need to hold out for 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, the main fleet will use\Nits anti-fortress weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anti-fortress weapon?\NWhat could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Commence attack, minus 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All Publics, 3... 2... 1... 0!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What's up?\NHow far has the enemy closed in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! They're hiding in the debris of Side 4\Nas they continue to advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- They're now within beam attack range!\N- All right. Shoot them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.46,0:10:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Missiles! Main cannons! Beam cannons!\NPrepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy has created\Na powerful beam interference field!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rick Dom and Zaku forces,\Nprepare for enemy advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't that many enemy vessels.\NSwitch to missile attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Milva Fleet, move to left wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Harvard Force, stay in the rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tianem's main fleet will approach\Nfrom another direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.67,0:11:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The beam interference field is working!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! All vessels,\Nproceed at your own discretion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch our GM and Ball mobile suit forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile suits and G-Fighters,\Nbegin launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget, this is a joint operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall behind, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.37,0:11:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I only hope the Zanzibar's not here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla, launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Guncannon, taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the first shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And next up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai. Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla! I love ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,La Coque. Take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll be right back.\N- Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case, I want all women\Nmoved to the escape capsules!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the battle going that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Move it.\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.48,0:13:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Solomon will never fall.\NIt's just a precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.06,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in case something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,For Mineva, who has finally blessed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You spoke too loudly...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A little closer... Closer... That's the ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Life or death?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.02,0:14:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No one knows the outcome\Nuntil the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The only certainty is that\Nwith every beautiful sparkle in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...people, or even hundreds of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...are becoming debris\Nlittered through space.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are the mirrors ready?\N- Sir! About 4 minutes longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Solomon should detect us about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! You just realized they're hiding\Namong the debris of Side 1?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's the matter?!\N- It's Tianem's main fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch the satellite missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Send the battleship Gwaran and\Nsome Musais against their main fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Should we ask the 7th Division for backup?\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Help from Kycilia?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For such a minor skirmish...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be the laughingstock of all Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mirror deployment complete!\N- Attitude control vernier linkage system: OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Solar System target: Solomon's right flank!\NThe space gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,10 seconds to axis alignment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Interceptors approaching!\NAll ships, be alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore them! Hurry with focus alignment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,3... 2... Focus is now on target!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Solomon!? It's burning up! So that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of the Federation's new weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gate 6 has vanished!\NThe enemy's new weapon did this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing on radar!\NNo energy particle reactions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's some kind of laser?!\NFrom where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's main fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the Gwaran force headed there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is mega particle cannon 45.\NWhere should we be firing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no good.\NThe cartridge lock is shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Guntank has returned with level B damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The pilot is injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.20,0:17:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Guntank's retreat,\Nfighting strength is down 11 percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato's hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of injured people is increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me go and help the medics!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Permission granted.\NBaro, take over for Fraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Petty Officer Masaki!\NPrepare for a transfusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll feel better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I do anything to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring a unit of type AB blood\Nand a transfusion set.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy main fleet approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch all the satellite missiles\Nin orbit right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to give Hayato another unit\Nof blood after this one. Don't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming! It's a Dom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fraw Bow?\N- Stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You've fought more than enough already.\NNow it's time for you to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The others...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all fine.\NThey're out there fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so frustrating...\NI'm the only one in this sorry state.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even keep up\Nwith Ms. Sayla and Mr. Kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.13,0:18:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Hayato?!\NYou're doing a fine job too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to comfort me, Fraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I joined the White Base crew\NI've wanted nothing better...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...than to somehow beat Amuro.\NBut look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's different...\NHe's different from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,2nd and 6th Gattle combat squadrons,\Nno response! Gwaran, no response!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- La Coque. Could you get me more coffee?\N- Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull back all remaining mobile suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll wipe out the enemy\Nat Solomon's doorstep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're retreating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I force my way in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's where the new weapon got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Message from the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that one of our mobile suits\Nhas entered Solomon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Instruct all ships\Nto launch their mobile suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Titan calling all vessels!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Send out your GM and Ball\Nmobile suit assault teams!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Solomon's requesting reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The message is encrypted,\Nso we don't have any details...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...but Lady Kycilia's orders are\Nto head for Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah. Are you ready?\NYou're finally headed for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Zanzibar! Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.76,0:21:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Destination, Solomon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.59,0:21:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands to level 3 battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They finally left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least...\NI hope you live a long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Zenna here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:21:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling. Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't be silly! Solomon will never fall!\N- Then...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to escape\Nand go to my sister's Granada base.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that hopeless?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going fine. Don't worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.06,0:22:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of Mineva.\NMake sure she grows up strong, Zenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.17,0:22:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a military man...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a soldier who will uphold\Nthe Zabi family tradition...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.99,0:22:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Zenna! And take Mineva!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Assemble mobile suit forces on the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.05,0:22:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is about to land!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.87,0:22:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All remaining Rick Doms and Zakus!\NPrepare for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Gattle combat squadrons, launch\Nas soon as your missiles are reloaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Big Zam ready for combat?\NThe final battle is yet to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.65,0:23:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the Big Zam...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Dozle's mobile armor\Nbrushes aside the Federation Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When Lieutenant Sleggar's desperate attack\Nbreaks through the enemy's defense...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...Amuro witnesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...the shadow of hatred\Nthat dwells within Dozle's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.67,0:23:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NBig Zam's Last Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Zam's Last Stand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
